Class HuslColorSpace

java.lang.Object

      com.psddev.dari.util.HuslColorSpace
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class HuslColorSpace
extends ColorSpace

Human-friendly alternative to the HSL color space based on CIE LChuv.

The implementation is derived from the work by Alexei Boronine and Lajos Ambrus at https://github.com/boronine/husl.
